 Q  The  answer  must  be  a  device  that  you  put  coins  into  to  make  it  work .  A  stove  is  not  a  device  that  you  put  coins  into .  A  water  fountain  is  not  a  device  that  you  put  coins  into .  A  desk  is  not  a  device  that  you  put  coins  into .  A  purse  is  a  place  to  put  coins ,  but  not  a  device .  A  jar  is  a  container ,  but  not  a  device  that  you  put  coins  into  to  make  it  work .  A  vending  machine  is  a  device  that  you  put  coins  into  to  make  it  work .  So  the  answer  is  vending  machine  ( not  given  in  the  options ).

 Q  The  answer  must  be  a  consequence  of  having  too  many  cocktails .  Having  fun  is  not  a  consequence  of  having  too  many  cocktails .  Dr unken ness  is  a  state  of  being ,  not  a  thing  you  have  in  the  morning .  Hang over  is  a  common  consequence  of  having  too  many  cocktails ,  so  the  answer  is  hang  over  ( d ).

 Q  The  answer  must  be  a  direction  that  the  car  is  going .  Alabama  is  in  the  south  and  New  York  is  in  the  north ,  so  the  car 's  goal  is  to  head  north .  Head  north  is  the  same  as  heading  north ,  so  the  answer  is  heading  north  ( c ).  Speed  up  and  go  fast  are  not  the  goal  of  the  car ,  but  the  car  might  be  going  fast  to  reach  its  goal .  So  the  answer  is  heading  north  ( c ).

 Q  The  answer  must  be  something  that  is  printed  with  ink  and  distributed  daily .  A  fountain  pen  is  a  writing  tool ,  not  something  that  is  printed .  Squ id  is  a  type  of  sea  creature ,  not  something  that  is  printed .  Book  is  a  type  of  publication ,  but  not  something  that  is  printed  daily .  Newspaper  is  something  that  is  printed  with  ink  and  distributed  daily .  So  the  answer  is  newspaper  ( c ).

 Q  The  answer  must  be  a  reason  that  is  relevant  to  why  people  stop  caring  about  their  problems .  No  problems  is  not  a  reason  for  people  to  stop  caring  about  their  problems .  Better  themselves  is  a  way  to  solve  problems ,  not  why  people  stop  caring .  Face  problems  is  a  way  to  deal  with  problems ,  not  why  people  stop  caring .  Learn  from  each  other  is  a  way  to  solve  problems ,  not  why  people  stop  caring .  Become  disillusion ed  is  a  reason  why  people  stop  caring  about  their  problems ,  as  they  lose  interest  in  the  effort  to  solve  them .  So  the  answer  is  become  disillusion ed  ( e ).

