 Q  The  answer  must  be  a  place  where  you  can  easily  find  a  map .  A  truck  stop  is  a  place  where  you  can  easily  find  a  map ,  as  it  is  a  common  place  for  people  to  stop  and  rest .  An  amusement  park  is  not  a  place  where  you  would  typically  find  a  map .  An  atlas  is  a  book  that  contains  maps ,  but  not  a  place .  Mall  is  a  place  where  you  can  find  many  things ,  but  not  a  map .  Gas  station  is  a  place  where  you  can  easily  find  a  map ,  as  it  is  a  common  place  to  stop  for  directions .  So  the  answer  is  gas  station  ( e ).

